==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: chintzy
<hw>chintzy</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>resembling chintz or
decorated with chintz.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>of very poor quality.</def>
<mark>[informal]</mark>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> bum, cheap, cheesy, crummy, punk, sleazy, tatty,
tinny, chinchy.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>stingy; miserly.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> cheap.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>chin-up</ent>⟦br⟧
